mjc.tree

Class View

  • java.lang.Object
    • mjc.tree.View

  • public class View
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that creates a tree view of Appel's TREE code. Can be used as follows: 

         tree.View viewer = new tree.View("Name of function");
     viewer.addStm(treeBody);
     viewer.expandTree();
